=== [aiModels.ts:122] 🟠P1 ===
问题描述
stream() 方法返回 `Promise<void>`，正常完成时 promise 永远不会 resolve（因为没有 `resolve()` 调用），只通过 `onChunk('', true)` 通知完成。异常时 promise 也不 reject，仅调用 `onError`。调用方若 `await stream(...)` 会永久挂起。

代码片段
```javascript
async stream(...): Promise<void> {
  try {
    await window.electronAPI.ai.stream(prompt, {...})
  } catch (error: unknown) {
    const msg = error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error)
    if (onError) onError(msg)
    // promise 永远不会 resolve/reject，调用方 await 会永久挂起
  }
}
```

修复建议
添加 `resolve` 使 promise 可终结：
```javascript
return new Promise<void>((resolve) => {
  let finished = false
  removeChunkListener = window.electronAPI.ai.onStreamChunk((chunk) => {
    if (chunk.done) {
      if (!finished) { finished = true; resolve() }
    } else {
      onChunk(chunk.content, false)
    }
  })
  removeErrorListener = window.electronAPI.ai.onStreamError((error) => {
    if (onError) onError(error)
    if (!finished) { finished = true; resolve() }
  })
  window.electronAPI.ai.stream(prompt, {...}).catch((e: any) => {
    if (onError) onError(e.message)
    if (!finished) { finished = true; resolve() }
  })
})
```
